{"tid":2121152,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會、何君堯大搞無罩宴","createTime":"2020-07-23T06:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T06:40:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6d01611ab634d310c9690296735d013e045e3aeb","tid":2121152,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:40:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200723/ZY6RTRRGSDG24FOR4FY722JBLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FZY6RTRRGSDG24FOR4FY722JBLQ%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=41a0ff1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FZY6RTRRGSDG24FOR4FY722JBLQ%2F&h=b4ee24d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200723/ZY6RTRRGSDG24FOR4FY722JBLQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n工聯會、何君堯大搞無罩宴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bQQt050VtD8USkwU8q8c98KN2S0=/1176x514/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DJ4CGFIPM455UJBLVIQSEH4H3E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbQQt050VtD8USkwU8q8c98KN2S0%3D%2F1176x514%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDJ4CGFIPM455UJBLVIQSEH4H3E.gif&h=f749fd21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工聯會鄧家彪7月2日與多名大媽在無罩宴中熱舞慶回歸。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】多名建制派議員涉嫌知法犯法，網上傳出多張照片，顯示行政會議成員黃國健、已報名參選立法會的工聯會鄧家彪等，月初出席該會在黃大仙富臨皇宮舉行的慶回歸晚宴時，在進食以外時間脫下口罩四處交談，甚至上台唱歌、致辭、祝酒，涉嫌違反法例《預防及控制疾病規例》第599F章。鄧回應其他傳媒時稱席上無人感染武漢肺炎，並稱「法規上應該係冇問題」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：共用廁所 隆亨院舍兩員工染疫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n枱距不足1.5米涉違法<br />\n<br />\n據包括fb專頁「黃大仙連儂場」等網上資料，工聯會黃大仙地區服務處7月2日於黃大仙新光中心富臨皇宮舉辦「慶回歸」晚宴，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/smMNi06iq4r-ah5g9djchlHQEgY=/907x337/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GVCMSKDIUI42VE726O3O6JT4YM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsmMNi06iq4r-ah5g9djchlHQEgY%3D%2F907x337%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGVCMSKDIUI42VE726O3O6JT4YM.gif&h=f9164b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網傳何君堯7月中旬大宴親朋不設防，華記老闆楊官華及藝人楊明等人亦有出席。<br />\n<br />\n7月2日港府尚未再次收緊社交限制，每枱餐桌人數沒上限，但仍然要求每枱距離1.5米，顧客非進食時要戴口罩，否則違反法例。鄧回覆立場新聞時則承認，晚宴是在黃大仙富臨舉行，主要宴請街坊，他以嘉賓身份出席。他指當晚工聯會有為出席者量體溫、提供搓手液；但被問到有否依足指示戴口罩，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n翻查鄧家彪及黃國健的fb專頁，不時提醒市民戴口罩預防武漢肺炎非常重要。鄧家彪最近也多次落區派口罩，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌知法犯法的建制派還有何君堯，網上流傳，他在7月中旬曾在酒樓大宴親朋，主題為「君事。。。。。。。。。。。。"}]}